We can create a node only when we need it by using new, instead of pre-allocating a fixed amount of memory.

new keyword:-
Can be used with struct or class.
Struct:-
<Struct name>* <object name> = new <Struct name>;
Class:-
<Class name>* <object name> = new <Class name>(args for constructor);
